exercises.name: Squats
instructions: Stand with feet shoulder-width apart.
Lower your body by bending your knees.
Keep your back straight and chest up.
Push through your heels to return to the starting position.

exercises.name: Bench Press
instructions: Lie on a flat bench with your feet planted on the ground.
Grip the barbell slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.
Lower the barbell to your chest, keeping your elbows at a 45-degree angle.
Push the barbell back up to the starting position.

exercises.name: Pull-ups
instructions: Hang from the pull-up bar with your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.
Pull your body up until your chin is above the bar.
Lower yourself back down with control to complete one rep.

exercises.name: Deadlifts
instructions: Stand with your feet hip-width apart, with the barbell over your mid-foot.
Bend at your hips and knees and grab the barbell with an overhand grip just outside your legs.
Keep your chest up, back straight, and core engaged as you stand up, bringing the barbell to hip level.
Lower the barbell back down by pushing your hips back and bending your knees.
